  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  roomPresences:
  - roomTag: Kitchen
    spawnPoint: {fileID: 1504204976}
    animationTrigger: sit_counter
    dialogNodes:
    - npcLine: You are feeding body that doesn't belong to you
      responses:
      - 1.Then whoose it is?
      - 2.Shut up
      nextNodeIndex: 01000000ffffffff
      responseEvents: []
    - npcLine: Its ours, you just wear it better
      responses:
      - 1.Maybe You are right
      - 2.Stop saying that
      nextNodeIndex: ffffffffffffffff
      responseEvents: []
  - roomTag: Hallway
    spawnPoint: {fileID: 727389525}
    animationTrigger: idle
    dialogNodes:
    - npcLine: You don't need to watch all those horror movies, just stay here with
        me and watch
      responses:
      - 1.What do you mean?
      - 2.Leave me alone
      nextNodeIndex: 01000000ffffffff
      responseEvents: []
    - npcLine: Look at those sad faces, those depraved acts. Humanity is broken
      responses:
      - 1.We are not so diffrent after all
      - 2.How can you judge us monster
      nextNodeIndex: ffffffffffffffff
      responseEvents: []
  - roomTag: Bedroom
    spawnPoint: {fileID: 874157711}
    animationTrigger: lie_bed
    dialogNodes:
    - npcLine: All those nightmares? Are you not tired of them?
      responses:
      - '1.I am, I''m so tired of this. '
      - 2.I have them beacuse of You
      nextNodeIndex: 0100000002000000
      responseEvents: []
    - npcLine: I can help You, just listen to me
      responses:
      - 1.I trust you
      - 2.I don't trust you
      nextNodeIndex: ffffffffffffffff
      responseEvents: []
    - npcLine: Remember, I am Your only friend
      responses:
      - 1.I hate You
      - 2.You are the only one, who didnt leave me
      nextNodeIndex: ffffffffffffffff
      responseEvents: []
  - roomTag: Bathroom
    spawnPoint: {fileID: 631983620}
    animationTrigger: idle
    dialogNodes:
    - npcLine: Try to wash those bloody hands with something sharp
      responses:
      - 1.Blood is not real
      - 2.I see blood everywhere
      nextNodeIndex: ffffffff01000000
      responseEvents: []
    - npcLine: Its all beacuse of bad things You did
      responses:
      - 1.It's my punishment
      - 2.I didn't do anything
      nextNodeIndex: ffffffffffffffff
      responseEvents: []
  - roomTag: Staircase
    spawnPoint: {fileID: 235897306}
    animationTrigger: sit_railing
    dialogNodes:
    - npcLine: Watch ur back, you don't know what is hiding in the dark
      responses:
      - 1.I'm not affraid of You
      - 2.I can feel those eyes on my skin
      nextNodeIndex: 01000000ffffffff
      responseEvents: []
    - npcLine: I'm not talking about myself, there are more of US
      responses:
      - 1.Just leave me alone
      - '2.Please don''t hurt me '
      nextNodeIndex: ffffffffffffffff
      responseEvents: []
  - roomTag: LivingRoom_Table
    spawnPoint: {fileID: 591809749}
    animationTrigger: sit_chair
    dialogNodes:
    - npcLine: You used to sit here with your family
      responses:
      - 1.They are all gone, I miss them sometimes
      - 2.They left me, I hate them
      nextNodeIndex: 0100000002000000
      responseEvents: []
    - npcLine: I can help you see them again. Just listen to me
      responses:
      - 1.Are you serious? I would love to
      - 2.I don't belive You
      nextNodeIndex: ffffffffffffffff
      responseEvents: []
    - npcLine: Lets revenge on them togheter
      responses:
      - 1.I won't cooperate with You in any scenario
      - 2.We will make them beg for mercy
      nextNodeIndex: ffffffffffffffff
      responseEvents: []
  - roomTag: LivingRoom_TV
    spawnPoint: {fileID: 1057427899}
